Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:14.58,DTB-Default,Commander,0,0,0,,This is the command car. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:15.62,DTB-Default,Commander,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:20.46,DTB-Default,Commander,0,0,0,,Do you read me, Tahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.27,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I don't know... I can't describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.89,DTB-Default,Commander,0,0,0,,I can't hear you. Was there an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:28.52,DTB-Default,Commander,0,0,0,,Where are the other reconnaissance members?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:32.22,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I told you I can't describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:40.47,DTB-Default,Commander,0,0,0,,We cannot confirm your vitals or coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:41.26,DTB-Default,Commander,0,0,0,,Your location?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:44.26,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I'm headed towards the Fukagawa entrance point,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:47.33,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,passing Kiyosubashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:50.92,DTB-Default,Commander,0,0,0,,We're coming to rescue you. Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:53.28,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Don't come! You mustn't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:09.79,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,This isn't a place man should tread.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.38,0:01:19.84,DTB-Default,Commander,0,0,0,,Say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:20.64,DTB-Default,Commander,0,0,0,,This is the command car...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:00.12,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Oh, good...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:06.76,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:43.05,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.28,DTB-Default,Tenant,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.17,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:53.12,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Oh, how commendable of you, taking out the garbage in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:56.78,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,If only everyone else followed the rules like you, Li-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.61,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,That cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:02.38,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,I've seen this black one around here lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:06.07,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,It's probably the same one that's been rummaging through the garbage at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.22,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.22,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What a naughty cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:13.09,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,It seems like someone's been feeding him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.55,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,You better watch out, too. Pets are forbidden here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.12,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:18.16,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Off to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:19.65,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No, I'm going to my part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.43,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,It better not be a sleazy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.56,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.25,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'm running late, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:27.62,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:33.89,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, don't they eat anything with four legs in your country, besides tables?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:36.63,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I haven't tried it myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.83,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,It might taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.73,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:43.94,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Alright, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.55,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Hey! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:49.33,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Wait... Hey, you stupid cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.70,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.04,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,One hundred and forty yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.00,Location,,0,0,0,,{\be1\bord0\shad0\fs30\c&H464B4C&\fax0.05\frx2\fry4\pos(621,279)\frz15.574}School Visitation Day Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:47.42,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Li-kun, Li-kun, Li-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:48.18,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:51.51,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Can you deliver this to the annex?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.27,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Annex?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:55.98,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,You know, to Consultant Tahara's place in front of the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.88,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Isn't a consultant a high-ranking position?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:00.93,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:06.77,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,It looks like he's been sleeping there and not going home. I have no idea what he's working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:09.93,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,They say he was once an important scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:14.79,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Before he came here, he was apparently conducting strange research abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:18.20,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Heard about the Hell's Gate First Reconnaissance Troop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:21.03,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Rumor has it that he was the sole survivor of the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.65,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Reconnaissance troop...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:26.28,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,They say he lost his soul in that gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:30.39,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know whether it's true or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.86,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Consultant, there's a package for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.89,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Consultant Tahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:40.98,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,It's unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:47.57,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Um, the factory manager asked me to hand you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:52.84,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:53.80,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.16,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Aren't you being paid by the hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.61,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.15,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Get back to work if you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:14.25,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.10,DTB-Default,Attendant,0,0,0,,Your room number is 802.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:18.56,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:33.27,DTB-Default,Ruuko,0,0,0,,In order to avoid bankruptcy, you need that man's power, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.37,DTB-Default,Ruuko,0,0,0,,Let's hurry and obtain it if that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:39.66,DTB-Default,Ruuko,0,0,0,,Isn't that why I'm here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:43.47,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,There are necessary procedures one must follow in order to conduct business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:45.42,DTB-Default,Ruuko,0,0,0,,Those procedures are a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:50.40,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Honestly speaking, I hate you contractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:57.00,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Do you know why we're breathing the same air, even though it stinks of your bad breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.21,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Reluctantly, all for the sake of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:05.93,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Furthermore, do you know why you're acting indifferently, despite what I just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:12.18,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,It's because you're a piece of garbage that can't manage to live without the protection of your patron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.42,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,If you understand where I'm going with this, don't ever second-guess me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:21.18,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Where's the bottle opener?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.60,DTB-Default,Ruuko,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.84,DTB-Default,Ruuko,0,0,0,,I better work hard so you don't throw me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:32.52,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,If he declines, we'll move on to the next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:34.45,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,We'll keep going until he says yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.53,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,If he still won't concede, we'll persuade him by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.90,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,That's how I handle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:54.91,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Hey! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:06.31,DTB-Default,Man,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:12.97,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:19.19,DTB-Default,Office lady,0,0,0,,Consultant? There's a call for you from the headmaster of Nishi Toyotama Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:19.89,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.66,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.21,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Do you have a Japanese driver's license?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.88,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I'm asking if you can drive a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.12,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:34.51,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fscy140\fscx80\pos(885,581)}Episode Three
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:34.51,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(1174,682)}A New Star Shines in the Dawn Sky... \N(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:44.18,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Geez, you're heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:49.66,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Two employees from Meyer & Hilton checked into a hotel at Shinjuku thirty minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.17,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,How are things on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:56.20,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Why is this person here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:09:00.92,DTB-Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Well, you were under the custody of your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:05.47,DTB-Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,but ever since your mother passed away, you've been living with your father, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.54,DTB-Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,In that case, your legal guardian is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:10.86,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I don't consider a person who only comes home once a month as my legal guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:17.87,DTB-Default,Headmaster,0,0,0,,My, we're lucky the notice came to the school and not to the police, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:21.29,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that I didn't commit arson!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:26.35,DTB-Default,Headmaster,0,0,0,,However, the person who witnessed it said you were burning trash at the back of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.49,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I wasn't the one who burned it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:30.59,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,It was burning right in front of me before I realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:35.11,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Why... Why don't you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.59,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,We'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:39.99,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,We're going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.68,DTB-Default,Headmaster,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:45.16,DTB-Default,Headmaster,0,0,0,,Mr. Tahara, I still have more to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.82,DTB-Default,Headmaster,0,0,0,,Mr. Tahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.04,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Are you telling the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:56.46,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Was the trash burning on its own before you realized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:09:59.65,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Is this the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:03.97,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Do these occurrences happen frequently?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.75,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Did you eat something strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:11.13,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,When did you start acting unconsciously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.85,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Talk about a rarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:16.40,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,for you to be talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:21.08,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.03,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.90,DTB-Default,Girl B,0,0,0,,What? A chauffeur? You're like a celebrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.21,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Are you going anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:37.43,DTB-Default,Girl B,0,0,0,,The same place, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:42.41,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:45.11,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:46.20,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:47.30,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:48.84,DTB-Default,Girls,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.50,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.12,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,It doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.84,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Hurry up and return to the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:03.39,DTB-Default,Girl B,0,0,0,,You've recently been acting as if your mind has been drifting, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:07.06,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I think my soul has been drifting on occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.25,DTB-Default,Girl B,0,0,0,,Tired from doing too many chores?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:11.94,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,You don't have a mother, do you, Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:13.78,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:16.44,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,But you have a father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:18.24,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Yes and no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.37,DTB-Default,Girl B,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.38,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,Are you doing the cooking, Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.46,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.79,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I'm also eating by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.93,DTB-Default,Girl B,0,0,0,,Your dad doesn't come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:29.87,DTB-Default,Girl B,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:32.69,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:39.13,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,Why don't you eat dinner at my place from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:40.26,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:46.47,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,I have a brother and sister, so it's kind of noisy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:50.28,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,Meals taste better when there are people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:53.50,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,Papa and Mama will be glad to have you, so come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:55.51,DTB-Default,Girl B,0,0,0,,Yuka, what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:58.38,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,We won't have any food left if you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:11:59.28,DTB-Default,Girl B,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:06.07,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:07.49,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:12.45,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,My father might come back today for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:13.34,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:14.52,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:18.00,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,A lot of things happened, so I'll probably be lectured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.01,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.14,DTB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,Next time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:23.98,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Sorry, Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:26.53,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:57.88,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you before you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:01.80,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I've been saying that I won't return to your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:06.25,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,In that case, we'll be forced to change our attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.92,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:08.88,DTB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.73,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:36.92,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,We're proceeding to the next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:39.72,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:40.83,DTB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,The daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:01.77,DTB-Default,Attendant,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:06.78,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.77,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'd like to pay for both of these items.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.90,DTB-Default,Attendant,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:19.82,DTB-Default,Truant officer,0,0,0,,So what are you doing at this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.51,DTB-Default,Truant officer,0,0,0,,Middle school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:23.29,DTB-Default,Truant officer,0,0,0,,Are your parents with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:26.07,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.63,DTB-Default,Truant officer,0,0,0,,Young lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.74,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:31.65,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'm her older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:47.32,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Hey, don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:52.16,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,What? Did that person tell you to keep an eye on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.05,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,If he did, tell him this:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:55.53,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,You're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:56.57,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.12,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I don't want to see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.71,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Don't ever come back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.31,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.92,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.43,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Do you feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:21.20,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Let's go home. I'll walk you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.36,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I don't want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:30.95,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I don't want to go back to that dark and empty room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:38.50,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Then let's play until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:39.25,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:51.22,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,It's a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.99,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Can you close your eyes for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:57.67,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.51,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.27,DTB-Default,Watchman,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.25,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:56.17,DTB-Default,Owner,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:17:04.16,DTB-Default,Owner,0,0,0,,The capricious patissier's parfait with fresh fruit and choux chocolat, topped with rice dumplings and almond seeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:14.13,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I see. So you're from China, Li-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:16.26,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,You speak Japanese well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:21.01,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,It may not look like it, but I've been living abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:24.56,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,My family lived in Africa until I entered grade school...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:28.98,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Okay, as an exception,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:31.48,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I'll show it only to you, Li-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.81,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Take a close look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:37.67,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:41.96,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,The glow was stronger in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:49.17,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,It gradually became darker, and now it even disappears from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:55.21,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,When I was a child, Papa told me there was an amulet inside that was protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.13,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Your father told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.68,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Was he a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.34,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:07.04,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.92,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:09.60,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,A scientist?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.55,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What kind of research did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.09,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.68,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Li-san, why did you come to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.25,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,To study abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.07,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Do you have any brothers, sisters, or family?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:23.35,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:29.32,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I see. You're the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.26,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,It's almost time for the first train.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:43.60,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,It's moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:47.34,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,but it isn't the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:56.71,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Li-san, you're kind of like an... older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.83,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,We're going into the next alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.70,DTB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Huh? Li-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:12.04,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.35,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Don't think! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:31.77,DTB-Default,Foreman,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't come in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:34.33,DTB-Default,Workers,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:27.66,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Yes, Kirihara speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.48,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Boss, it's a new star!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:32.89,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,A star has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:44.33,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Moratorium, those who have deferred the conditions of their contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:49.29,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Power that doesn't come with an immediate price requires a larger compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:53.85,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The withering affection is a one-way ticket with no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:58.75,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Its destination, either heaven or hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:03.76,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Her scream will become a new flare, and her fate will be sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:08.24,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Everything will be engulfed by the roaring flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.45,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hededed&}Episode Four A New Star Shines in the Dawn Sky... (Part Two)